display_long_description:
FULL VERSION RELEASE!!
Feb 2025: 30% Discount Applies

Its not just a Maze; its a Quest!

Enter the captivating realm of Maze Quest, where each unexpected turn presents fresh challenges, hidden treasures, and unexpected surprises! Your journey begins with L1: Training Day, a quick and exciting intro to get you geared up and familiar with the mechanics of this thrilling VR experience.

Navigate through intricate mazes, collecting objects and dodging obstacles, all while racing against the clock. Keep your eyes sharp. Hidden ammo and hourglass objects can give you extra time and ammunition, but you'll need precision to shoot them and claim the rewards. Your primary objective is to reach the portal gate before the time expires. The portal will instantly end the level, propelling you to greater challenges.

Stay fully engaged with intuitive VR controls:
The Right Controller: Your score and photon count, so you’re always in the know.

The Left Controller keeps you focused with the time remaining, ensuring you don't lose track of your race against the clock.

Each maze is uniquely designed to test your reflexes, puzzle-solving skills, and navigation prowess. Can you conquer the labyrinth and unlock its hidden secrets? With increasing complexity and dynamic challenges, Maze Quest delivers a high-energy VR adventure.

Dare to take on the maze? The time is running out.

Enter Maze Quest and prove your skills in the ultimate VR maze experience!

Skyboxes by Blockade Labs
Music by John Campanella and others
